@startuml SC-47-Notifications
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Configurer Notifications (Employe)

object Employe
object "Interface Notifications" as InterfaceNotif
object "Service Notifications" as ServiceNotif
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Service Audit" as ServiceAudit

Employe --> InterfaceNotif : 1: acceder("Notifications")
InterfaceNotif --> ServiceNotif : 2: obtenirPreferencesNotifications(employeId)
ServiceNotif --> BaseDonnees : 3: executerRequete(preferences)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceNotif : 3.1: donneePrefs
ServiceNotif --> InterfaceNotif : 4: afficher(parametres)
InterfaceNotif --> Employe : 4.1: montrer(options)

Employe --> InterfaceNotif : 5: activer_desactiver(notification_type)
InterfaceNotif --> ServiceNotif : 6: mettreAJourPreferencesNotifications({type, activee})
ServiceNotif --> BaseDonnees : 7: mettreAJourEnregistrement(prefs)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceNotif : 7.1: ok

ServiceNotif --> ServiceAudit : 7.2: enregistrerAction("PREFERENCES_NOTIFICATIONS_MISES_A_JOUR")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 7.3: sauvegarderLog()

ServiceNotif --> InterfaceNotif : 8: succes()
InterfaceNotif --> Employe : 9: afficher("Preferences mises a jour")

note right of ServiceNotif
Types notifications:
- Emails
- SMS
- Push
- Dashboard alerts
- Frequence (immediat, quotidien, hebdo)
end note

@enduml
